rose & apricot hair milk


$10.00






4 fl oz. - $26.00
1 fl oz. - $10.00








leave-in hydration for natural shine and moisturizing
This light, leave-in hair milk nourishes and protects hair with nine certified-organic oils and extracts. Nutrient-rich hydration helps repair sun damage. May be used as a light-hold styling product, or just to moisturize, defrizz and add shine. Perfect for dry or damaged hair. Apply to towel-dried hair and style as desired. Safe for color treated hair. 4 fl oz.
Made with 9 certified-organic ingredientsGluten-free



key ingredients



rose flower oil - softens and nourishes hair
apricot oil - treats dryness
rosehip seed oil - antioxidant; soothes scalp; hydrates hair
borage oil - replenishes lipid content
moringa seed extract - protects against environmental pollutants; strengthens hair





properties



untangles and eliminates frizz
strengthens hair and builds volume
leaves hair healthy and manageable





usage



good for making hair more manageable
perfect for styling and creating natural healthy shine
great for revitalizing hair throughout the day
provides the perfect hydration to protect and soften hair





directions



apply to damp or dry hair, focusing on damaged or frizzy areas such as the ends
follow with any John Masters Organics styling products





ingredients
Aqua (water), aloe barbadensis leaf juice*, glycerin, behentrimonium methosulfate, cetearyl alcohol, capric caprylic triglycerides, helianthus annuus (sunflower) seed oil*, panthenol, aniba rosaeodora (rosewood) wood oil, pelargonium graveolens (rose geranium) oil, citrus aurantium dulcis (orange) peel oil, prunus armeniaca (apricot) kernel oil, moringa pterygosperma seed extract, mongongo oil (schinziophyton rautanenii kernel oil), linum usitatissmum (linseed) seed oil*, borago officinalis (borage) seed oil*, rosa rubginosa (rose hip) seed oil, theobroma grandiflorum (cupuacu) seed butter, butyrospermum parkii (shea butter), rosa damascena (rose) flower distillate, chamomilla recutita (matricaria) flower extract*, calendula officinalis flower extract *, camellia sinensis leaf extract (green tea extract)*, rosmarinus officinalis (rosemary) leaf extract*, urtica dioica (nettle) extract*, sodium pca, soy protein, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate
 
* Certified Organic





