hair spray


$10.00






2 fl oz. - $10.00
8 fl oz. - $24.00


NOTE: Due to shipping restrictions we can only ship this product via ground transportation.






usda-organic, flexible hold with a great natural aroma
Our all-natural, plant-based hairspray offers an excellent, flexible hold with no flaky residue. Six organic ingredients suffuse hair with beneficial nutrients while delivering an all-day hold with a light, citrus scent. Safe for color-treated hair. 8 fl oz. See our Hair Spray in action during New York Fashion Week, Fall 2016!
Made with 6 certified-organic ingredientsGluten-free



key ingredients



aloe vera - nourishes & protects
acacia senegal gum - provides hold; adds volume
xanthan gum - provides hold; protects against humidity
glycerin - protects & prevents breakage
bergamot - strengthens hair & adds shine





properties



gives a touchable, medium hold
non-drying, lightweight formula
never sticky or flaky





usage



good for all hair types
fights frizz & protects against humidity
perfect for styling curly & straight hair
great for daily use
safe for color-treated hair





directions



spray into damp or dry hair and style as desired
lift hair and spray at the root for increased volume
for a firmer hold, mist over hair again after styling





ingredients
Aloe barbadensis (aloe vera) leaf juice*, alcohol denat.*, acacia senegal gum*, saccharomyces ferment*, glycerin*, citrus aurantium (bergamot) fruit oil*, xanthan gum
 
* Certified Organic





